… we were ready for it… and she brought it! We 🫶🏼 @taylorswift The @taylorswift Eras tour was absolutely incredible! It was one of the highlight’s of my life to watch my precious niece, Savannah, live out her dream of seeing Taylor in concert! We had the best time from making sure we had enough glitter to sparkle as bright as possible, singing on the way, eating lunch to enjoying every last minute of the concert. Core memory made! Being an Aunt is one of many big blessings the Lord has given me!
Until next time Taylor ❤️ 
(My dress is @vicidolls)
